screen_desc: The screenshot displays a Telegram app interface. At the top, it shows the username "Tri Nguyen" with an online status and a profile picture of a cat. Below, there are various settings options including "Data and Storage," "Power Saving," "Chat Folders," "Devices," and "Language" (set to English). Further down, it lists features like "Telegram Premium," "My Stars," "Telegram Business" (marked as new), and "Gift Premium." The bottom section includes a "Help" category with options to "Ask a Question," access "Telegram FAQ," and view the "Privacy Policy." The app version is noted at the bottom.
